# Changelog

## [Unreleased]

## [0.18.1] - 2025-11-05

### Changed
- api/dependents: static parameter to skip findseries expansion
- constant operator: support naive timestamps and handle tzaware query bounds
- find_last_values: use series interval to bound search instead of 3000-day limit
- integration: optimized find_last_values with sliding window for backward search

### Fixed
- search/isformula: sql operator precedence bug in `and` expressions
- migrate: rebuild dependency table migration for 0.18.1
- migrate: ensure form_history table has userid column
- helper/periods-map: missing periods
- http/doc: standardized endpoint documentation format
- integration: flow series with ffill handling
- date operator: docstring to reflect actual behavior
- test/api: test_tree_api after byatpath default changed

## [0.18.0] - 2025-08-29

### Added
- api:
  - group_formula: federation support
  - bindings_for: federation support  
  - group_rename: working integrity-preserving group rename
  - depends: track (reverse) formula dependencies
  - oldformulas: access older versions of a formula (with user field)
  - group_eval_formula: evaluate group formulas on-the-fly
- operators:
  - date-filter: new operator with cronrule support
  - group-from-series: create groups from series
  - group-add-series: dedicated operator for adding series to groups
  - cumprod: cumulative product operator
  - series: keepnans parameter to preserve NaN values
- tsio:
  - group_log: avoid crashing on non-primary groups
  - insertion_dates: support for limit parameter
  - info: implement info protocol for formulas
- groups: change group bindings db representation
- types: implement closed vocabularies with Literal
- vocabulary: update timezones, period offsets and calculation methods
- search/group/by.formula: include bound groups in formulas result set
- http/client: type annotations

### Changed
- switch from sqlalchemy to sqlhelp throughout
- operators:
  - conditionals: accept nan as input
  - constant: highlight impossibility of naive constant expressions
  - integration: first 2 inputs are series names
  - start-of-month: set hour, minute and second to zero
  - tzaware: ensure results are localized in UTC
  - options: ensure options are kept in various operators (naive, tzaware, comparators, resample, upsample, rolling, cumsum, asof, time-shifted, slice)
- api:
  - depends: always return a list
  - register_formula: forbid tzawareness change if we have dependents
- tsio:
  - interval: return None when no series referenced
  - register_formula: do not record non-changes
  - find: fix group kind of results
- schema: 
  - switch off binary protocol for multi-statement initialization
  - bound-groups: add missing column in unique constraint
- helper:
  - find_tz: also record when crossing tzaware operator
  - regroup migration helpers
  - fix_day_period: correct d vs D period issue
- gfuncs/group-add: do not raise error when no group provided
- http: use choices rather than enums for constrained string fields
- migrate: add Freq and valid timezones for 0.18.0
- vocabulary: fix date-filter, block-staircase, FreqType transformation
- pkg: bump holidays version

### Fixed
- test/bug: tzaware operator returning false metadata info
- test/integration: issue with delete + rename flow
- test/constant: failure of .interval with constant series
- operators/date-filter: optimize index filter with pandas builtin
- tsio/group-formula: fix tzawareness detection
- api/formula_depth: fix return type when no source
- depth: fix federation bug by attributing -1 to primary depth
- pytype: fix invalid annotation error
- vocabulary: fix double migration
- test: fix strange pytest golden error

### Removed
- operators: remove by.source (following tshistory change)

## [0.17.0] - 2025-02-25

### Added
- operators/upsample: new operator for upsampling
- operators/bysource: provide bysource filter to findseries
- api/eval_formula: tz option
- migrate/interval: prepare migration for intervals
- funcs: add BasketName, Source and MetaKey for proposals
- funcs/doc: add examples for <, >, = operators

### Changed
- operators/resample: integrate upsample mechanisms
- operator/findseries: use other sources for remote series support
- use new configuration object and codecs module
- conftest: use tempconfig
- schema: register version at init-db time
- test: switch PostgreSQL port to 5434 for server usage
- pkg: bump holidays and pycountry versions

### Fixed
- operator/findseries: make it work with remote series
- search/isformula: fix signature (used by tsview)
- conftest: fix DATADIR and remove unused fixture

### Removed
- cli: retire the whole module

## [0.16.2] - 2024-10-24

### Added
- operator/today: re-introduce today operator (distinct from now)

### Fixed
- operators: do not lower the freq
- operators/holidays: fix lack of explicit horizon (like constant)
- operators/resample: 
  - backout change helping upsampling case (ffill by default)
  - use fill option parameter in resample
- test-operators: silence deprecation warnings

### Changed
- ci: move to heptapod

## [0.16.1] - 2024-09-04

### Fixed
- tsio/update: inhibit formula patching capability
- test/operator/add: document odd corner case

### Changed
- test/api: move test to api level (better placement)

## [0.16.0] - 2024-08-06

### Added
- operators/tzaware: new operator to convert series to timezone-aware
- tsio/rename: propagate option (default True) for bw compatibility
- api/formula: remote parameter to cross federation boundaries (default True)
- api/formula_depth: cross instance boundaries
- http: document api points, introduce required roles on relevant routes
- search: add missing type signatures for UI
- pandas 2.x support

### Changed
- operators/today: renamed to "now" (might reintroduce different today later)
- operators/resample: fix behavior when upsampling (use series freq not provided freq)
- tsio/history: recast infrastructure in terms of insertion_dates + get (remove complex optimizations)
- api/formula: switch default value of display to true
- findseries operator handling:
  - depth calculation now goes through findseries
  - expansion now goes through findseries
  - dependents now account for findseries operator
  - formula-components and insertion-dates work with findseries
- pkg: update holidays package
- build: remove tsview (no longer provides extension to test)

### Fixed
- tsio/get: honor api contract wrt query boundaries
- tsio/get: loop detection to avoid self-referencing formulas
- tsio/register_formula: verify well-formedness of formula keywords
- operators/findseries: correct handling of naive parameter
- operators/by.basket: remove unnecessary parameters
- helper/replace_findseries: make it take and return tree, use cn object
- tsio/rename: defer metadata updates after iterating (avoid useless computations on error)
- search: make depth calculus compatible with empty findseries
- test/rename: fix test transaction control
- reduce deprecation warnings

### Removed
- cli: retire old migrations

