### Fixed
- migrate: brown-paper-bag fix
- operators/group_series: fix exit case with empty series
- migrate/formula-schema: avoid crash on encounter with broken series
- bug: formula lost tz-awareness with priority operator (3+ members, last one add operator out of bounds)

### Changed
- migrate: reduce verbosity

### Removed
- cli/shell: retire (tshistory shell does the job)

