  - integration: integrate flow series to last known value of stock series
  - doy: day of year operations
- tsio:
  - support for first/latest_insertion_date
  - complete metadata support for formula and bound formulas groups
  - helper tools to list primaries and autotrophics
  - formula_stats: improved counting of repetitions
- group/formula: metadata protocol for autotrophic group formulas
- formula/expanded: shownames parameter to prune tree (dual of stopnames)
- cli:
  - fix-group-metadata: tool to fix existing groups
  - migration to fix formula and bound group formula metadata
  - resurrect group tables creation

### Changed
- editor: moved to tsview (too much flexibility for own good)
- interpreter: only expose operators with docstring
- group/hijacking:
  - more correct formula expansion with low level helpers
  - optimization to reduce computation and memory use
  - cache only named nodes higher in formula tree
- api/register-formula-bindings: fix docstring
- tsio/register-formula-bindings:
  - ensure series and groups exist
  - ensure tz-compatible groups
  - nocheck parameter to avoid chicken-egg with metadata
- http: better json representation for bindings_for api point

### Fixed
- group/hijacking: getargs not properly propagated through overloaded get method
- group/insertion_dates: remove irrelevant groups from bindings
- bound-formula-groups: fix recursion error
- bound-group/idates: fix limit case excluding first idate
- http/client: correctly handle type errors at register_formula time
- cli/rename-operators: groups not properly handled

### Removed
- cli: retire old migration

