  - group operators with docstrings
  - http api support for group formulas and bound formulas
- helper/expanded: stopnames argument to limit expansion
- cli:
  - update-metadata: specify one series and show tzawareness
  - migration to groups command for upgrading instances
- api: type hints and docstrings for group operations
- blueprint: host formula part of tshistory http api (server side)

### Changed
- groups: rename group-add to better name
- cli/typecheck: use pdbshell arg properly
- tsio/register-formula: preserve previous user metadata on update

### Fixed
- tsio/history: 
  - fix issues with formula and lower bounds on insertion dates
  - handle case with lower bounds and no history (common with autotrophic operators)
- operators: document skipna keywords where relevant
- evaluator: cleanup imports
- interpreter: fix wrong indentation

### Removed
- cli: retire old migration command

## [0.8.1] - 2021-01-19

### Fixed
