- history: fix autotrophic operators history naming issues
  - handle multiple autotrophic operators in same formula
  - automatic history handling via @func decorator
  - proper name forging using operator name, parameters and call arguments
  - handle unevaluated subexpressions in auto operator arguments
  - handle positional arguments fed as keywords
  - special handling for impure operators (e.g. today) using interpreter-scoped cache
- interpreter: silence pandas deprecation warning
- history/auto: fix name handling blunder in _groupby

### Changed
- history/auto: use local cache for computed names
- history/auto: delegate name handling to interpreter

## [0.7.2] - 2020-07-30

